<p>Hi <%= @signature.name %>,</p>

<p>Parliament are going to debate the petition you signed &ndash; &ldquo;<%= @petition.action %>&rdquo;.</p>

<p><%= link_to nil, petition_url(@signature.petition) %></p>

<p>The debate is scheduled for <%= short_date_format(@signature.petition.scheduled_debate_date) %>.</p>

<p>Once the debate has happened, we&apos;ll email you a video and transcript.</p>

<p>Thanks,<br />
<%= t("petitions.emails.signoff_prefix") %><br />
<%= link_to nil, home_url %></p>

<p><small>You&apos;re receiving this email because you signed this petition. Unsubscribe: <%= link_to 'unsubscribe', unsubscribe_signature_url(@signature, @signature.unsubscribe_token) %></small></p>
